{
  "texts": [
    "Unsupervised loss is computed in order to generate clusters of representations.",
    "While they also test on language identification, the dialect identification part is done on Swiss German dialect.",
    "Jurgens et al. [2017] use a character-based seq2seq model to map dialects.",
    "The models used for language identification are RNNs with GRU.",
    "Criscuolo and Aluisio [2017] use character n-grams to identify language groups."
  ]
}